            <scopecontent id="aspace_5deae0e7fa1e91c7894e715321d1c2f4">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The Hoyt Curtiss Pease Papers consist of materials pertaining to Yale Crew, with an emphasis on the Yale-Harvard regattas. The papers were written and collected by Hoyt C. Pease, grandson of Julian W. Curtiss, the Yale Crew captain in 1878. Pease was manager of the Yale Crew of 1934 and served as regatta chairman from 1940-1974.</p>
            </scopecontent>
